ectively.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1679, \"end\": 1682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9983687373543424, \"rank\": 0.001023456407377692, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1685, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenny Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}, {\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"score\": 0.9999999862577625, \"rank\": 1.3310539698430266e-08, \"text\": \"Seville\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latter athlete cut a disappointing figure after the race as he told SportsMax he had felt discomfort in his groin during the race.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's 100m final was a far cry from the women's 100m final on August 3, as the winner, Lyles, and the eighth-placed Seville were separated by just 0.12 seconds.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1995, \"end\": 2000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9999999767810552, \"rank\": 2.3215431861099532e-08, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 2024, \"end\": 2031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"score\": 0.9999999862577625, \"rank\": 1.3310539698430266e-08, \"text\": \"Seville\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gap was closer than the distance between women's 100m champion Julien Alfred and silver medallist Sha'Carri Richardson, who clocked 10.72 and 10.87 seconds respectively.\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2171, \"end\": 2191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles will try to further enhance his case in the \\\"fastest man\\\" argument when he faces the starter in heat six of the men's 200m from 2.30 pm (TT time) on August 5.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2387, \"end\": 2389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"score\": 0.9999993324504385, \"rank\": 6.044728492354381e-07, \"text\": \"TT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\"}]}]}"